summary: This appears to be an email forwarding a PDF attachment related to a court document concerning Ghislaine Maxwell. The attachment is a final release document from the United States District Court.

persons.name: Maxwell Ghislaine
persons.context: Named in the title of the attached PDF court document, which is a final release.

events.title: Email forwarding Maxwell court document
events.description: An email was sent with an attachment titled 'Final_Release-40897182-Maxwell-Ghislaine- United_States_District_Court_GB.PDF'.

keyFacts: A final release court document concerning Ghislaine Maxwell was circulated via email on December 31, 2019.
The document originates from the United States District Court.
